<plot>This 2-part documentary is about the making of the 1998 Peter Weir film, _Truman Show, The (1998)_(qv). There are interviews with a few of the cast &amp; crew members that all inform us on how great this film is, and was to make. The original screenplay is discussed, along with the risky casting of Jim Carrey for the lead, and plenty of other information for lovers of the film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248802</url></doc>
